  ('elementary-d0d1b9a2-moex-00050', 'elementary-d0d1b9a2', 'elementary-d0d1b9a2-moex-114-b3f42868', 'sub-elementary-d0d1b9a2-01', NULL, 'single_choice', 'Whichofthefollowingbestdescribestheauthor’sattitudeaboutboardgames?', '["Bitter", "Anxious", "Supportive", "Aggressive"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:30:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e1455ee2159f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "c91e411dad10", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114010", "c": "511", "s": "0102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公民與英文", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 50, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "會計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-d0d1b9a2-moex-00051', 'elementary-d0d1b9a2', 'elementary-d0d1b9a2-moex-114-34c7f7f6', 'sub-elementary-d0d1b9a2-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列文句「」中的成語用法，何者正確？', '["當一個人做事「行不由徑」，信用和形象都已被打折扣", "她講話總是「拾人牙慧」，充滿個人獨特的想法與見解", "上司若為人正直，行事端正，相信下屬也會「群起效尤」", "工作要先計畫周全再開始執行，才能收「事半功倍」之效"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:30:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "dc62ea810384", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ad957d5f3d5b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114010", "c": "511", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "會計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-d0d1b9a2-moex-00052', 'elementary-d0d1b9a2', 'elementary-d0d1b9a2-moex-114-34c7f7f6', 'sub-elementary-d0d1b9a2-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列選項句中的「窮」字，何者意義與其他三者不同？', '["明經博覽，無不「窮」究", "君子固「窮」，小人窮斯濫矣", "兩家子孫各長大，他年「窮」達毋相忘", "多有之者富，少有之者貧，至無有者「窮」"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:30:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "dc62ea810384", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ad957d5f3d5b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114010", "c": "511", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "會計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-d0d1b9a2-moex-00053', 'elementary-d0d1b9a2', 'elementary-d0d1b9a2-moex-114-34c7f7f6', 'sub-elementary-d0d1b9a2-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列情境語句，何者使用錯誤？', '["那雙「骨碌碌」的眼睛轉啊轉，不知在打什麼主意", "芭蕾舞者「活跳跳」的表演，看得觀眾都目不轉睛", "吃完這碗湯麵後，全身「熱呼呼」的，真是舒服啊", "此刻小張的心緒一定是「亂紛紛」的，別打擾他了"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:30:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "dc62ea810384", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ad957d5f3d5b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114010", "c": "511", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "會計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-d0d1b9a2-moex-00054', 'elementary-d0d1b9a2', 'elementary-d0d1b9a2-moex-114-34c7f7f6', 'sub-elementary-d0d1b9a2-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列文句「」中的成語，運用恰當的是：', '["太魯閣風景「美輪美奐」，吸引遊客們駐足觀賞", "對於公司未來的發展，千萬不可「目無全牛」胡亂想像", "懲處違法亂紀的「始作俑者」，才能達到殺雞儆猴的效果", "夫妻之間「相敬如賓」，往往會讓旁人以為他們感情不好"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:30:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "dc62ea810384", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ad957d5f3d5b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114010", "c": "511", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "會計"}'::jsonb, NULL)
